00:11:00,044 --> 00:11:03,172
只有你身上的跳蚤会为你送葬
and only your fleas will mourn you.

185
00:11:06,317 --> 00:11:08,251
我有教养
I'm not worthless.

186
00:11:08,319 --> 00:11:10,549
而且我身上没跳蚤
And I don't have fleas.

187
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:17,284
快点,阿布 我们回家吧
[sighs] Come on, Abu. Let's go home.

188
00:11:23,334 --> 00:11:26,462
无赖,叫化子
 Riffraff, street rat

189
00:11:26,537 --> 00:11:28,869
我不信
 I don't buy that

190
00:11:28,939 --> 00:11:32,705
只要他们看清楚
 If only they'd look closer

191
00:11:32,777 --> 00:11:36,975
难道他们只看见个穷孩子
 Would they see a poor boy

192
00:11:37,047 --> 00:11:38,776
不,先生
 No, siree

193
00:11:40,885 --> 00:11:44,286
他们会发现
 They'd find out

194
00:11:44,355 --> 00:11:48,121
还有很多东西
 There's so much more

195
00:11:48,192 --> 00:11:51,355
在我身上
 To me 

196
00:11:55,699 --> 00:11:56,688
[叹息声]
[sighs]

197
00:11:56,801 --> 00:12:00,638
总有一天,阿布, 事情会有所改变
Some day, Abu, things are gonna change.

198
00:12:00,638 --> 00:12:02,706
我们会变得富有,住在皇宫里
We'll be rich, live in a palace,

199
00:12:02,706 --> 00:12:07,044
不再有任何麻烦
and never have any problems at all.

200
00:12:07,044 --> 00:12:08,944
[天亮了]
[roosters crowing]

201
00:12:10,748 --> 00:12:12,483
我从来没有被这么羞辱过
I've never been so insulted.

202
00:12:12,483 --> 00:12:16,387
阿赫麦德王子 你这么快就走了?
Oh, Prince Achmed. You're not leaving so soon, are you?

203
00:12:16,387 --> 00:12:18,556
祝你走运,能把她嫁出去
Good luck marrying her off.

204
00:12:18,556 --> 00:12:21,150
噢!茉莉.
Oh! Jasmine.

205
00:12:22,493 --> 00:12:24,518
茉莉!
[Sultan] Jasmine!

206
00:12:24,595 --> 00:12:26,495
茉莉!
Jasmine!

207
00:12:26,564 --> 00:12:28,589
茉莉!
- Jasmine! - [snarling]

208
00:12:28,666 --> 00:12:30,793
该死的!拉扎
Confound it, Rajah.

209
00:12:34,138 --> 00:12:37,341
原来这就是阿赫麦德王子 大发雷霆的原因
So, this is why Prince Achmed stormed out.

210
00:12:37,341 --> 00:12:38,831
父亲
Oh, Father.

211
00:12:38,909 --> 00:12:41,742
拉扎只是和他逗着玩 对吧,拉扎?
Rajah was just playing with him. Weren't you, Rajah?

212
00:12:41,812 --> 00:12:44,114
你只是和那个衣冠楚楚
You were just playing with that overdressed,

213
00:12:44,114 --> 00:12:46,878
自恋狂的阿赫麦德王子逗着玩,对吗?
self-absorbed Prince Achmed, weren't you?

214
00:12:46,951 --> 00:12:48,384
[both laughing]

215
00:12:49,420 --> 00:12:50,751
[clears throat]

216
00:12:50,821 --> 00:12:55,315
亲爱的,你不能拒绝每一个前来求婚的人
Dearest, you've got to stop rejecting every suitor who comes to call.

217
00:12:55,392 --> 00:12:59,260
法律上规定..你必须嫁给一个王子.
The law says you must be married to a prince...

218
00:12:59,363 --> 00:13:01,297
在你下一个生日
by your next birthday.

219
00:13:01,332 --> 00:13:02,822
法律是错的
The law is wrong.

220
00:13:02,900 --> 00:13:05,164
你只剩下三天了
You've only got three more days.

221
00:13:05,236 --> 00:13:08,899
父亲,我讨厌被逼迫着嫁人
Father, I hate being forced into this.

222
00:13:08,973 --> 00:13:12,272
如果我嫁人,那一定是为了爱
If I do marry, I want it to be for love.

223
00:13:12,343 --> 00:13:14,504
茉莉...
Jasmine...

224
00:13:14,578 --> 00:13:17,775
不只是因为那条法律
it's not only this law.

225
00:13:18,883 --> 00:13:24,446
我不能照顾你一辈子, 并且,我...
I'm not going to be around forever, and, well, I...

226
00:13:24,521 --> 00:13:28,184
我只想确认有人能照顾你
I just want to make sure you're taken care of.

227
00:13:28,259 --> 00:13:29,658
早点做准备
Provided for.

228
00:13:29,727 --> 00:13:32,457
请你理解我
Please try to understand.

229
00:13:32,529 --> 00:13:36,884
我从没有自己拿过主意 我也未曾有过真正的朋友
I've never done a thing on my own. I've never had any real friends.

230
00:13:36,884 --> 00:13:37,926
[嘟囔声]
[grumbles]

231
00:13:38,002 --> 00:13:39,594
除了你,拉扎.
Except you, Rajah.

232
00:13:41,338 --> 00:13:44,241
我甚至从没踏出过这宫殿的围墙
I've never even been outside the palace walls.

233
00:13:44,241 --> 00:13:46,709
但是,茉莉,你是公主啊
But, Jasmine, you're a princess.

234
00:13:46,777 --> 00:13:49,712
那我不想当公主了
Then maybe I don't want to be a princess anymore.

235
00:13:49,780 --> 00:13:52,647
我...我...
Oooh! I... I...

236
00:13:52,716 --> 00:13:55,810
真主啊,但愿你没有女儿
Allah forbid you should have any daughters.

237
00:13:55,886 --> 00:13:57,353
嗯?
Hmm?

238
00:14:08,232 --> 00:14:11,463
我不知道她这是象谁
I don't know where she gets it from.

239
00:14:11,535 --> 00:14:15,528
她妈妈可没这么挑剔
Her mother wasn't nearly so picky.

240
00:14:15,606 --> 00:14:18,131
贾法尔.
Oh! Ah, Jafar.

241
00:14:18,208 --> 00:14:21,769
我最信任的大臣
My most trusted advisor.

242
00:14:21,845 --> 00:14:24,748
我确实需要你给我出个主意
I am in desperate need of your wisdom.

243
00:14:24,748 --> 00:14:27,512
我生来就是为您效劳的,国王陛下
My life is but to serve you, my lord.

244
00:14:27,584 --> 00:14:29,279
就是求婚的事
It's this suitor business.

245
00:14:29,353 --> 00:14:31,844
茉莉不愿选一位丈夫
Jasmine refuses to choose a husband.

246
00:14:31,922 --> 00:14:34,914
-我已经绞尽脑汁了. -绞尽脑汁!
- I'm at my wit's end. - Awk! Wit's end!

247
00:14:34,992 --> 00:14:36,857
[laughing] Oh!

248
00:14:38,095 --> 00:14:41,496
-吃块饼干吧,亲爱的波利
- Have a cracker, pretty Polly. - [Jafar laughs]

249
00:14:41,565 --> 00:14:44,864
陛下对付不会讲话的动物 确实有办法啊
Your Majesty certainly has a way with dumb animals.

250
00:14:44,935 --> 00:14:46,095
[grumbles]

251
00:14:46,170 --> 00:14:50,664
那么对于这个棘手的问题
Now, then, perhaps I can divine a solution

252
00:14:50,741 --> 00:14:52,868
也许我可以用占卜术 找出办法来
to this thorny problem.

253
00:14:52,943 --> 00:14:54,535
如果有人可以帮忙的话, 那就是您了
If anyone can help, it's you.

254
00:14:54,611 --> 00:14:59,742
需要借用一下那颗神秘的蓝宝石
But it would require the use of the mystic blue diamond.

255
00:14:59,817 --> 00:15:02,718
噢,我的戒指?
Oh. Uh, my ring?

256
00:15:02,786 --> 00:15:05,222
但它可是我的祖传宝贝啊
But it's been in the family for years.

257
00:15:05,222 --> 00:15:08,487
要想为公主找到一个求婚者 它是必需的
It is necessary to find the princess a suitor.

258
00:15:08,559 --> 00:15:10,356
别担心
Don't worry.

259
00:15:10,427 --> 00:15:14,090
一切都会好的
Everything will be fine.

260
00:15:14,164 --> 00:15:16,724
一切都会...好的
Everything will be... fine.

261
00:15:16,800 --> 00:15:18,893
宝石
The diamond.

262
00:15:18,969 --> 00:15:21,494
在这儿,贾法尔.
Here, Jafar.

263
00:15:21,572 --> 00:15:25,008
不管你要什么我都给你
Whatever you need will be fine.

264
00:15:25,075 --> 00:15:27,805
您真是太伟大了,国王陛下
You are most gracious, my liege.

265
00:15:27,878 --> 00:15:31,541
现在,您可以玩您的小玩具了
Now, run along and play with your little toys, hmm?

266
00:15:31,615 --> 00:15:35,142
对,那真是太好了
Yes. That will be pretty good.

267
00:15:36,854 --> 00:15:38,344
[spits, coughs]

268
00:15:38,422 --> 00:15:40,515
我再也无法忍受了!
I can't take it anymore!

269
00:15:40,591 --> 00:15:46,797
如果再硬塞给我那些发霉的、 讨厌的饼干的话...
If I gotta choke down on one more of those moldy, disgusting crackers...

270
00:15:46,797 --> 00:15:48,890
我打!打!
Bam! Whack!

271
00:15:48,966 --> 00:15:50,331
安静些,拉戈
Calm yourself, lago.

272
00:15:50,401 --> 00:15:52,803
我就要篡夺他的王位了
Then I'd grab him around the head. Whack!

273
00:15:52,803 --> 00:15:56,707
不久国王就是我了, 不再是那个糟老头子了
Soon I will be sultan, not that addle-pated twit.

274
00:15:56,707 --> 00:16:01,076
到时候我会把饼干塞进他的喉咙里
And then I stuff the crackers down his throat.

275
00:16:01,145 --> 00:16:02,669
Ha, ha!

276
00:16:18,295 --> 00:16:19,557
[whining]

277
00:16:19,630 --> 00:16:22,690
对不起,拉扎
Oh, I'm sorry, Rajah.

278
00:16:22,766 --> 00:16:25,929
我不能再呆在这儿, 象现在这样过一辈子
But I can't stay here and have my life lived for me.

279
00:16:28,005 --> 00:16:30,064
我会想你的
I'll miss you.

280
00:16:37,448 --> 00:16:38,437
[whimpers]

281
00:16:38,515 --> 00:16:40,278
再见了
Goodbye.

282
00:16:47,357 --> 00:16:51,020
[vendors calling out]

283
00:16:51,095 --> 00:16:52,756
好,阿布.开始吧
Okay, Abu. Go.

284
00:16:54,565 --> 00:16:58,763
尝尝这个吧,真是太好吃了
Try this. Your taste buds will dance and sing.

285
00:16:58,836 --> 00:17:00,929
[squeaking]

286
00:17:01,004 --> 00:17:03,165
将你的爪子拿开
- Get your paws off that. - [taunting]

287
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:04,298
你...
Why, you...

288
00:17:04,374 --> 00:17:08,140
滚开,你这只讨厌、肮脏的猴子!
Get away from here, you cursed, filthy ape!

289
00:17:09,680 --> 00:17:11,341
再见
Goodbye.

290
00:17:11,415 --> 00:17:14,714
干的好,阿布.
- Nice going, Abu. - [cooing]

291
00:17:14,785 --> 00:17:17,015
早饭准备好了
Breakfast is served.

292
00:17:20,757 --> 00:17:22,816
可爱的小姐,买个壶吧
Pretty lady, buy a pot.

293
00:17:22,893 --> 00:17:25,225
再没有这么好的铜壶和银壶了
No finer pot in brass or silver.

294
00:17:25,295 --> 00:17:27,763
甜枣,卖甜枣了,还有无花果
Sugar dates. Sugar dates and figs.

295
00:17:27,831 --> 00:17:30,026
甜枣,还有开心果
Sugar dates and pistachios.

296
00:17:30,100 --> 00:17:31,897
这位小姐喜欢项链吗?
Would the lady like a necklace?

297
00:17:31,969 --> 00:17:34,529
只有这你这样美丽的姑娘 才配得上这条漂亮的项链
A pretty necklace for a pretty lady.

298
00:17:34,605 --> 00:17:36,039
新鲜的鱼!
Fresh fish!

299
00:17:36,039 --> 00:17:37,529
我们捕鱼,你们买鱼!
We catch 'em, you buy 'em!

300
00:17:37,608 --> 00:17:39,269
不.不对
Oh, no. I don't think so.

301
00:17:39,343 --> 00:17:40,742
- Oh! - [gulping]

302
00:17:40,811 --> 00:17:43,746
对不起
- Excuse me. - [gulps]

303
00:17:43,814 --> 00:17:45,679
[belches]

304
00:17:46,950 --> 00:17:49,919
真的很抱歉
I'm really very sorry.

305
00:17:51,321 --> 00:17:52,788
Wow.

306
00:17:57,661 --> 00:18:00,027
Uh-oh.

307
00:18:00,097 --> 00:18:02,156
喂?喂?
Hello? Hello?

308
00:18:05,202 --> 00:18:07,670
你一定是饿了
Oh, you must be hungry.

309
00:18:07,738 --> 00:18:09,399
拿去吧
Here you go.

310
00:18:09,473 --> 00:18:12,636
你最好把钱给我
You'd better be able to pay for that.

311
00:18:12,709 --> 00:18:13,911
钱?
Pay?

312
00:18:13,911 --> 00:18:16,004
没人能从我的货车里偷走东西
No one steals from my cart.

313
00:18:16,079 --> 00:18:18,843
对不起,先生 我没带钱
Oh, I'm sorry, sir. I don't have any money.

314
00:18:18,916 --> 00:18:20,349
-小偷! -求求你...
- Thief! - Please...

315
00:18:20,417 --> 00:18:24,444
如果你让我进到皇宫里 我可以从国王那里拿钱给你
If you let me go to the palace, I can get some from the Sultan.

316
00:18:24,521 --> 00:18:26,790
你知道对于小偷是如何惩罚的吗?
Do you know what the penalty is for stealing?

317
00:18:26,790 --> 00:18:28,519
别!别,求您了!
No! No, please!

318
00:18:28,592 --> 00:18:31,662
谢谢,您真是个好人 很高兴你帮我找到她了
Thank you, kind sir. I'm so glad you found her.

319
00:18:31,662 --> 00:18:33,653
我一直在到处找你
I've been looking all over for you.

320
00:18:33,730 --> 00:18:35,823
-你在干什么? -快点配合一下
- What are you doing? - Just play along.

321
00:18:35,899 --> 00:18:38,265
你,认识这个女孩?
You, uh, know this girl?

322
00:18:38,335 --> 00:18:40,929
是的,她是我.
Sadly, yes. She is my sister.

323
00:18:41,004 --> 00:18:42,596
她有点疯疯癫癫的
She's a little crazy.

324
00:18:42,673 --> 00:18:45,542
她说她认识国王.
She said she knew the Sultan.

325
00:18:45,542 --> 00:18:48,375
她认为这只猴子就是国王
She thinks the monkey is the Sultan.

326
00:18:50,380 --> 00:18:54,043
英明的国王,我愿为您效劳
O wise Sultan, how may I serve you?

327
00:18:54,117 --> 00:18:57,109
[gibberish]

328
00:18:57,187 --> 00:18:59,485
悲剧,您说呢?
Tragic, isn't it?

329
00:18:59,556 --> 00:19:01,581
但是没什么伤害
But no harm done.

330
00:19:01,658 --> 00:19:04,491
现在,,咱们走吧 该去看医生了.
Now, come along, sis. Time to go see the doctor.

331
00:19:04,561 --> 00:19:07,130
医生，你好
Oh, hello, Doctor. How are you?

332
00:19:07,130 --> 00:19:10,759
-不,不,不.不是他 -快点,国王
- No, no, no. Not that one. - Come on, Sultan.

333
00:19:10,834 --> 00:19:13,132
[gibbering, gasping]

334
00:19:14,004 --> 00:19:15,198
什么?
Huh? What?

335
00:19:16,506 --> 00:19:18,736
回来,你这个小偷!
Come back here, you little thieves!

336
00:19:20,177 --> 00:19:21,838
[爆炸声]
[explosion]

337
00:19:22,779 --> 00:19:25,646
请恕我冒犯,你这个烂人,
With all due respect, Your Rottenness,

338
00:19:25,716 --> 00:19:29,311
难道我们要等真正的风暴吗?
couldn't we just wait for a real storm?

339
00:19:29,386 --> 00:19:31,377
闭嘴,拉戈.再快点
Save your breath, lago. Faster.

340
00:19:32,356 --> 00:19:35,154
遵命,你个大魔头
Yes, O mighty Evil One.

341
00:19:35,225 --> 00:19:36,283
[panting]

342
00:19:37,694 --> 00:19:40,720
到时候了
Part, sands of time.

343
00:19:40,797 --> 00:19:44,961
告诉我谁能进入奇幻谷
Reveal to me the one who can enter the cave.

344
00:19:45,035 --> 00:19:48,368
对!对!
Yes! Yes!

345
00:19:48,438 --> 00:19:50,838
就是他
There he is.

346
00:19:50,907 --> 00:19:53,273
深藏不露的家伙
My diamond in the rough.

347
00:19:53,343 --> 00:19:56,938
就是他?那个乡巴佬? 他就是我们要找的人?
That's him? That's the clown we've been waitin' for?

348
00:19:57,014 --> 00:20:03,283
我们派卫兵去请他来皇宫,是吗?
Let's have the guards extend him an invitation to the palace, shall we?

349
00:20:03,353 --> 00:20:04,945
对极了
Swell.

350
00:20:05,022 --> 00:20:06,717
[coughs]

351
00:20:06,790 --> 00:20:09,918
[sinister laughter]

352
00:20:09,993 --> 00:20:11,984
快到了
Almost there.

353
00:20:19,336 --> 00:20:22,772
我要谢谢你帮我拦住了那家伙
I want to thank you for stopping that man.

354
00:20:22,839 --> 00:20:24,500
不用谢
Uh, forget it.

355
00:20:25,742 --> 00:20:29,940
你是第一次来市场,对吗?
So, this is your first time in the marketplace, huh?

356
00:20:31,248 --> 00:20:32,875
有那么明显吗?
Is it that obvious?

357
00:20:32,949 --> 00:20:36,009
是啊,你确实有点与众不同
Well, you do kind of stand out.

358
00:20:37,421 --> 00:20:42,518
我是说,你不知道 阿古拉巴有多危险
I mean, uh, you don't seem to know how dangerous Agrabah can be.

359
00:20:42,592 --> 00:20:45,186
我学的很快哟
Hmm. I'm a fast learner.

360
00:20:45,262 --> 00:20:46,752
Wow.

361
00:20:47,397 --> 00:20:49,058
[chuckling] Hey.

362
00:20:50,667 --> 00:20:53,192
来.走这边
Come on. This way.

363
00:20:53,270 --> 00:20:56,330
小心别碰头
Whoa. Watch your head there.

364
00:20:56,406 --> 00:20:57,964
小心!
Be careful.

365
00:20:58,041 --> 00:20:59,838
你就住在这里?
Is this where you live?

366
00:20:59,910 --> 00:21:03,107
是.只有我和阿布,来去自由
Yep. Just me and Abu. Come and go as we please.

367
00:21:03,180 --> 00:21:05,148
难以置信
That sounds fabulous.

368
00:21:05,215 --> 00:21:09,481
还有呢,这里位置绝佳
Well, it's not much, but it's got a great view.

369
00:21:10,287 --> 00:21:13,415
皇宫看起来是多么壮观啊
Wow. The palace looks pretty amazing, huh?

370
00:21:13,490 --> 00:21:16,288
是很棒
Oh, it's wonderful.

371
00:21:16,360 --> 00:21:18,487
我想不出在那里面 是什么样
I wonder what it would be like to live there,

372
00:21:18,562 --> 00:21:21,053
有仆人服侍你
and have servants and valets.

373
00:21:21,131 --> 00:21:24,794
是啊.总有人告诉你要去哪儿、 该穿什么衣服
Oh, sure. People who tell you where to go and how to dress.

374
00:21:24,868 --> 00:21:27,336
比这里好
It's better than here.

375
00:21:27,404 --> 00:21:30,202
你总是要省吃俭用, 还要提防那些卫兵
You're always scraping for food and ducking the guards.

376
00:21:30,273 --> 00:21:32,503
这里你无法自己作主
You're not free to make your own choices.

377
00:21:32,576 --> 00:21:35,170
-有时你会觉得... -你只是...
- Sometimes you feel so... - You're just...

378
00:21:35,245 --> 00:21:37,509
...被困住了
[both]...trapped.

379
00:21:40,550 --> 00:21:43,849
你从哪儿来?
[clears throat] So, where are you from?

380
00:21:45,021 --> 00:21:46,579
这重要吗?
What does it matter?

381
00:21:46,656 --> 00:21:49,250
我从家里跑出来,我不想再回去了
I ran away and I am not going back.

382
00:21:49,326 --> 00:21:51,920
真的?怎么会呢?
Really? How come?

383
00:21:51,995 --> 00:21:53,656
为什么?你...
Why, you...

384
00:21:53,730 --> 00:21:57,996
我父亲非逼我嫁人
My father's forcing me to get married.

385
00:21:58,068 --> 00:22:00,866
那...那真是太可怕了
That's... that's awful.

386
00:22:01,938 --> 00:22:05,430
阿布!
- [Aladdin] Abu! - [angry squeaking]

387
00:22:05,509 --> 00:22:07,704
它说什么?
What?

388
00:22:07,778 --> 00:22:11,441
阿布说... 那不公平
Abu says, uh... that's not fair.

389
00:22:11,515 --> 00:22:12,607
什么?
What?

390
00:22:12,682 --> 00:22:15,082
-真的? -当然了
- Oh, did he? - Yeah, of course.

391
00:22:15,152 --> 00:22:19,022
阿布还说了别的什么吗?
And does Abu have anything else to say?

392
00:22:19,022 --> 00:22:22,626
我想,他想帮你做点什么
Well, uh, he wishes there was something he could do to help.

393
00:22:22,626 --> 00:22:24,685
天哪！
Oh, boy.

394
00:22:24,761 --> 00:22:26,388
Hmm.

395
00:22:26,463 --> 00:22:29,990
告诉他，那可太好了
Tell him that's very sweet.

396
00:22:32,202 --> 00:22:33,692
你在这儿
Here you are.

397
00:22:33,770 --> 00:22:37,274
-他们在抓我!是在抓你? -一定是我父亲派来的...
- [both] They're after me! After You? - My father must have sent them...

398
00:22:37,274 --> 00:22:38,536
-你相信我吗? -什么?
- Do you trust me? - What?

399
00:22:38,608 --> 00:22:41,634
-你相信我吗? -是...
- Do you trust me? - Yes...

400
00:22:41,711 --> 00:22:44,303
那么,跳!
Then jump!

401
00:22:48,885 --> 00:22:53,219
我们一直在相互较量,对吗? 叫化子?
We just keep running into each other, don't we, street rat?

402
00:22:54,124 --> 00:22:56,115
快跑!快!离开这!
Run! Go! Get out of here!

403
00:22:56,115 --> 00:22:58,700
快把这个东西给我拿开!
Get this thing off of me!

404
00:22:58,728 --> 00:23:01,665
-你等着进地牢吧,臭小子 -放开我
- It's the dungeon for you, boy. - Get me off

405
00:23:01,665 --> 00:23:02,996
放了他
Let him go.

406
00:23:03,066 --> 00:23:07,560
快看啊,一个叫化子
- Looky here, men. A street mouse. - [guards laugh]

407
00:23:07,637 --> 00:23:11,232
放开他,这是公主的命令
Unhand him, by order of the princess.

408
00:23:12,576 --> 00:23:14,373
茉莉公主
Princess Jasmine.

409
00:23:14,444 --> 00:23:16,207
-公主? -公主?
- The princess? - [Abu] Princess?

410
00:23:16,279 --> 00:23:19,339
你在皇宫外面干什么? 还和一个叫化子
What are you doing outside the palace? And with this street rat.

411
00:23:19,416 --> 00:23:23,216
那和你没关系 照我说的做,放开他
That's not your concern. Do as I command. Release him.

412
00:23:23,286 --> 00:23:27,518
遵命,公主, 只是这是贾法尔的命令
I would, Princess, except my orders come from Jafar.

413
00:23:27,591 --> 00:23:31,527
-您必须让他同意才行 -相信我,我会的
- You'll have to take it up with him. - Believe me, I will.

414
00:23:37,767 --> 00:23:39,667
贾法尔?
Jafar?

415
00:23:39,736 --> 00:23:41,533
噢,公主
Oh, Princess.

416
00:23:41,605 --> 00:23:44,039
贾法尔,我被卡住了
Awk! Jafar, I'm stuck.

417
00:23:44,107 --> 00:23:46,337
愿为您效劳
How may I be of service to you?

418
00:23:46,409 --> 00:23:49,742
卫兵刚在市场上抓走了个男孩, 是你的命令
The guards just took a boy from the market, on your orders.

419
00:23:49,813 --> 00:23:54,079
是您父亲让我负责 维持阿古拉巴的秩序
Your father has charged me with keeping peace in Agrabah.

420
00:23:54,150 --> 00:23:56,675
-那个男孩是个罪犯 -他犯了什么罪?
- The boy was a criminal. - What was his crime?

421
00:23:56,753 --> 00:23:58,084
憋死我了,贾法尔
I can't breathe, Jafar.

422
00:23:58,154 --> 00:24:01,749
当然是绑架公主了
Why, kidnapping the princess, of course.

423
00:24:01,825 --> 00:24:04,157
如果你能... 疼死了!
If you could just... Aah! That hurt!

424
00:24:04,227 --> 00:24:06,923
他没有绑架我, 是我自己跑出来的
He didn't kidnap me. I ran away.

425
00:24:06,997 --> 00:24:09,932
天哪!
Oh, dear.

426
00:24:10,000 --> 00:24:14,300
这太让我意外了 我要是早知道...
Oh, how frightfully upsetting. Had I but known...

427
00:24:14,371 --> 00:24:15,599
你是什么意思?
What do you mean?

428
00:24:15,672 --> 00:24:19,267
很不幸,那个男孩的判决 已经执行了
Sadly, the boy's sentence has already been carried out.

429
00:24:19,342 --> 00:24:20,809
什么判决?
What sentence?

430
00:24:20,877 --> 00:24:22,868
死刑
- Death. - [gasping]

431
00:24:22,946 --> 00:24:25,938
-杀头 -不
- By beheading. - No.

432
00:24:28,652 --> 00:24:32,053
我非常抱歉,公主
I am exceedingly sorry, Princess.

433
00:24:32,122 --> 00:24:34,818
你怎么能?
How could you?

434
00:24:34,891 --> 00:24:36,688
[weeping]

435
00:24:38,795 --> 00:24:40,558
[咳嗽声]
[coughing]

436
00:24:40,630 --> 00:24:44,589
[coughing, gasping]

437
00:24:44,668 --> 00:24:46,761
就这么走了?
So, how did it go?

438
00:24:46,836 --> 00:24:50,533
我想她会接受... 这个事实的
I think she took it... rather well.

439
00:24:51,808 --> 00:24:53,969
[Jasmine crying]

440
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:06,081
都是我的错,拉扎.
It's all my fault, Rajah.

441
00:25:08,725 --> 00:25:11,853
我连他的名字都不知道
- I didn't even know his name. - [Rajah murmuring]

442
00:25:30,246 --> 00:25:32,714
她是公主
She was the princess.

443
00:25:32,782 --> 00:25:35,148
我简直不敢相信
I can't believe it.

444
00:25:35,218 --> 00:25:37,550
我早应该看出来的, 看她有多笨
I must have sounded so stupid to her.

445
00:25:37,621 --> 00:25:40,021
阿拉丁!
[Abu] Yoo-hoo! Aladdin!

446
00:25:40,090 --> 00:25:41,421
你好!
Hello!

447
00:25:42,492 --> 00:25:44,221
阿布.下来.
Abu. Down here.

448
00:25:44,294 --> 00:25:46,455
[squeaking]

449
00:25:46,529 --> 00:25:48,554
快点,帮我逃出去
Come on, help me out of these.

450
00:25:48,632 --> 00:25:50,759
[斥责声]
[scolding]

451
00:25:54,972 --> 00:25:59,376
可是当时她遇到麻烦了 是啊,那是她自找的
Hey, she was in trouble. Ah, she was worth it.

452
00:25:59,376 --> 00:26:01,241
对,对,对
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

453
00:26:01,311 --> 00:26:03,404
别担心,我再也不会见到她了
Don't worry. I'll never see her again.

454
00:26:03,480 --> 00:26:06,916
我是个叫化子,对吗? 有条法律
I'm a street rat, remember? And there's a law.

455
00:26:06,983 --> 00:26:09,076
她必须嫁给王子
She's gotta marry a prince.

456
00:26:10,086 --> 00:26:13,522
她应该嫁给一个王子
- She deserves a prince. - Ta-da!

457
00:26:13,590 --> 00:26:15,649
我真是个傻瓜
I'm a, I'm a fool.

458
00:26:15,725 --> 00:26:19,661
孩子,如果你放弃的话 你就真是个大傻瓜
[man] You're only a fool if you give up, boy.

459
00:26:19,729 --> 00:26:20,991
你是谁?
Who are you?

460
00:26:21,064 --> 00:26:24,500
一个囚犯,象你一样
A lowly prisoner, like yourself.

461
00:26:24,567 --> 00:26:27,502
但如果我们合作的话,也许会得到很多
But together, perhaps we can be more.

462
00:26:27,570 --> 00:26:29,868
我正在听着呢
I'm listening.

463
00:26:29,939 --> 00:26:33,898
孩子,有一个谷名叫奇幻谷
There is a cave, boy, a Cave of Wonders,

464
00:26:33,977 --> 00:26:38,141
那里堆满了你永远 也想象不到的金银财宝
filled with treasures beyond your wildest dreams.

465
00:26:38,214 --> 00:26:39,943
Ooh!

466
00:26:40,016 --> 00:26:44,009
我敢打赌,那些财宝足以打动你的公主
Treasure enough to impress even your princess, I'd wager.

467
00:26:44,087 --> 00:26:46,723
贾法尔,能不能快点? 我快要闷死了
Jafar, can you hurry up? I'm dyin' in here.

468
00:26:46,723 --> 00:26:49,351
但是法律规定只有王子才能...
- [squawking] - But the law says only a prince can...

469
00:26:49,426 --> 00:26:52,328
你听说过"有钱能使鬼推磨"吗?
You've heard of the golden rule, haven't you?

470
00:26:52,328 --> 00:26:54,831
谁有钱谁就能制定法律
Whoever has the gold makes the rules.

471
00:26:54,831 --> 00:26:56,230
[wheezing laugh]

472
00:26:56,332 --> 00:26:59,597
你为什么会和我分享 这些金银财宝?
Why would you share all of this wonderful treasure with me?

473
00:26:59,636 --> 00:27:04,232
我需要一双年轻的腿 一个强壮的身体才能进到谷里
I need a young pair of legs and a strong back to go in after it.

474
00:27:04,307 --> 00:27:05,968
还有一个问题
Uh, one problem.

475
00:27:06,042 --> 00:27:08,101
那个谷在外面,我们却还在这里
It's out there. We're in here.

476
00:27:08,178 --> 00:27:12,945
事情远非看起来那样简单
Uh-uh. Things aren't always what they seem.

477
00:27:14,017 --> 00:27:15,814
那么...
So...

478
00:27:15,885 --> 00:27:17,944
一言为定?
do we have a deal?

479
00:27:18,021 --> 00:27:20,387
我不知道
Oh, I don't know.

480
00:27:20,457 --> 00:27:22,322
[电闪雷鸣]
[thunder crashing]

481
00:27:31,334 --> 00:27:35,202
是谁把我吵醒了?
Who disturbs my slumber?

482
00:27:36,973 --> 00:27:40,204
是我,阿拉丁
Uh, it is l, Aladdin.

483
00:27:41,811 --> 00:27:44,279
进去吧
Proceed.

484
00:27:44,347 --> 00:27:48,374
除了神灯不要碰别的东西
Touch nothing but the lamp.

485
00:27:48,451 --> 00:27:51,682
记住,孩子,先把神灯给我
Remember, boy, first fetch me the lamp,

486
00:27:51,755 --> 00:27:55,714
你会得到奖赏的
and then you shall have your reward.

487
00:27:55,792 --> 00:27:57,555
走吧,阿布
Come on, Abu.

488
00:28:09,305 --> 00:28:10,397
[squeaking]

489
00:28:11,608 --> 00:28:14,236
你看到了吗
- Would you look at that! - [whimpering]

490
00:28:16,579 --> 00:28:21,482
只要得到这里的一点财宝， 我就会比国王还富
Just a handful of this stuff would make me richer than the Sultan.

491
00:28:21,551 --> 00:28:23,382
阿布!
Abu!

492
00:28:23,453 --> 00:28:24,545
[报怨声]
[whines]

493
00:28:24,621 --> 00:28:27,351
别...碰...任何东西
Don't... touch... anything.

494
00:28:27,423 --> 00:28:29,118
我们要找那神灯
We gotta find that lamp.

495
00:28:29,192 --> 00:28:30,853
[嘟囔声]
[grumbles]

496
00:28:46,810 --> 00:28:48,277
Huh?

497
00:29:01,190 --> 00:29:04,181
-阿拉丁! -阿布,别闹了行吗?
- Aladdin! - Abu, will you knock it off?

498
00:29:23,880 --> 00:29:25,780
[screeches]

499
00:29:26,916 --> 00:29:29,384
阿布,你疯了吗?
Abu, what are you, crazy?

500
00:29:31,688 --> 00:29:34,714
一个魔毯
A magic carpet.

501
00:29:34,791 --> 00:29:38,227
过来.快过来. 我们不会伤害你的
Come on. Come on out. We're not gonna hurt you.

502
00:29:46,269 --> 00:29:47,463
[screeches]

503
00:29:47,537 --> 00:29:51,107
别紧张,阿布.他不咬人
Hey, take it easy, Abu. He's not gonna bite.

504
00:29:51,107 --> 00:29:52,369
谢谢
Thanks.

505
00:29:52,442 --> 00:29:54,967
[squeaking]

506
00:30:00,350 --> 00:30:02,580
等一下.别走
Wait a minute. Don't go.

507
00:30:02,652 --> 00:30:04,586
也许你能帮我们
Maybe you can help us.

508
00:30:07,257 --> 00:30:09,418
Hey! Whoa!

509
00:30:09,492 --> 00:30:12,086
你看,我们正在找神灯
You see, we're trying to find this lamp.

510
00:30:13,563 --> 00:30:17,298
我想它知道神灯在哪儿
- I think he knows where it is. - [squeaks excitedly]

511
00:30:18,234 --> 00:30:20,964
[echoes]

512
00:30:31,981 --> 00:30:34,015
在这儿等着
[whispers] Wait here.

513
00:30:33,983 --> 00:30:35,712
[moaning]

514
00:30:40,623 --> 00:30:42,557
Oh!

515
00:31:07,583 --> 00:31:09,312
就是这个?
This is it?

516
00:31:09,385 --> 00:31:12,786
这就是我们翻山越岭 来到这儿要找的...
This is what we came all the way down here to...

517
00:31:12,855 --> 00:31:14,789
阿布!不要!
Abu! No!

518
00:31:15,792 --> 00:31:18,352
你背叛了我!
- [cave] lnfidels! - Uh-oh.

519
00:31:18,428 --> 00:31:23,491
你动了那些不能碰的财宝!
[cave] You have touched the forbidden treasure!

520
00:31:25,601 --> 00:31:31,005
你再也见不到阳光了!
Now you will never again see the light of day!

521
00:31:31,841 --> 00:31:32,830
Whoa!

522
00:31:57,100 --> 00:32:56,465
救命!救命!救命!
Help! Help! Help!

523
00:32:01,604 --> 00:32:03,162
抓到了!
Gotcha!

524
00:32:07,410 --> 00:32:08,843
飞毯,我们走
Carpet, let's move.

525
00:32:23,693 --> 00:32:25,558
阿布!
Abu!

526
00:32:25,628 --> 00:32:28,722
阿布,别慌
Abu, this is no time to panic.

527
00:32:29,632 --> 00:32:30,792
我也开始怕了
Start panicking.

528
00:32:30,867 --> 00:32:32,892
[both] Whoa!

529
00:32:39,776 --> 00:32:41,243
[Abu panting]

530
00:32:46,783 --> 00:32:48,546
[thunder cracks]

531
00:32:48,618 --> 00:32:50,449
[roaring]

532
00:33:01,998 --> 00:33:04,300
-救我出去 -把神灯扔过来
- Help me out. - Throw me the lamp.

533
00:33:04,300 --> 00:33:06,903
我坚持不住了,拉我一把
I can't hold on. Give me your hand.

534
00:33:06,903 --> 00:33:08,734
先给我神灯
First give me the lamp.

535
00:33:12,975 --> 00:33:14,966
[maniacal laughter]

536
00:33:15,044 --> 00:33:16,807
对!
Yes!

537
00:33:16,879 --> 00:33:19,313
终于得到了!
At last!

538
00:33:19,382 --> 00:33:22,146
- [wicked laughter] - [Aladdin struggles]

539
00:33:22,218 --> 00:33:23,879
你想干什么?
What are you doing?

540
00:33:23,953 --> 00:33:26,421
给你奖赏
Giving you your reward.

541
00:33:26,489 --> 00:33:29,356
你最终的奖赏
Your eternal reward.

542
00:33:31,527 --> 00:33:33,290
[screaming]

543
00:33:35,498 --> 00:33:36,795
[yelling]

544
00:33:45,374 --> 00:33:48,366
[roaring]

545
00:33:55,485 --> 00:33:57,282
[chuckling]

546
00:33:57,386 --> 00:33:58,944
它是我的了
It's mine.

547
00:33:58,988 --> 00:34:01,422
全是我的
It's all mine.

548
00:34:01,491 --> 00:34:04,360
我...哪去了?
I... where is it?

549
00:34:04,360 --> 00:34:05,554
不
No.

550
00:34:05,628 --> 00:34:07,721
不!
No!

551
00:34:13,503 --> 00:34:14,663
茉莉?
Jasmine?

552
00:34:17,507 --> 00:34:18,997
亲爱的
[Sultan] Oh, dearest.

553
00:34:19,075 --> 00:34:20,736
怎么了?
What's wrong?

554
00:34:20,810 --> 00:34:22,300
[sniffling]

555
00:34:22,378 --> 00:34:25,370
贾法尔他已经...
Jafar has...

556
00:34:25,448 --> 00:34:27,814
做了件很坏的事
done something terrible.

557
00:34:27,884 --> 00:34:30,717
来,来,我的宝贝
There, there, my dear.

558
00:34:30,786 --> 00:34:33,152
我们把它纠正过来
We'll set it right.

559
00:34:33,222 --> 00:34:36,749
现在,把一切都告诉我
Now, tell me everything.

560
00:34:38,561 --> 00:34:40,324
Oh.

561
00:34:40,396 --> 00:34:42,990
阿拉丁,醒醒
Aladdin. Wake up.

562
00:34:43,065 --> 00:34:44,692
阿拉丁
Aladdin.

563
00:34:44,767 --> 00:34:47,565
我的头
Oh! My head.

564
00:34:50,439 --> 00:34:51,997
我们被困住了
We're trapped.

565
00:34:52,074 --> 00:34:55,100
那个狗娘养的阴险家伙!
That two-faced son of a jackal!

