to escape the pressures of palace life.

1093
01:01:03,978 --> 01:01:06,913
但我真是一个王子
But I really am a prince.

1094
01:01:06,981 --> 01:01:09,506
你为什么才告诉我?
Why didn't you just tell me?

1095
01:01:09,584 --> 01:01:12,280
你知道...
Well, you know...

1096
01:01:12,353 --> 01:01:14,583
王室成员乔装改扮逃出皇宫
royalty going out into the city in disguise,

1097
01:01:14,655 --> 01:01:17,488
这听起来有些奇怪 你说呢?
it sounds a little strange, don't you think?

1098
01:01:17,558 --> 01:01:19,253
Hmm.

1099
01:01:19,327 --> 01:01:21,818
也不那么奇怪
Not that strange.

1100
01:01:43,785 --> 01:01:46,549
晚安,我英俊的王子
Good night, my handsome prince.

1101
01:01:46,621 --> 01:01:48,384
