For the first time in my life, things are starting to go right.

1106
01:02:22,957 --> 01:02:24,720
[yelling, struggling]

1107
01:02:27,228 --> 01:02:29,219
阿布.阿布
[muffled] Abu. Abu.

1108
01:02:29,297 --> 01:02:30,457
抓住他
Hold him.

1109
