你看上去有些憔悴 欢迎你,阿布王子
I'm afraid you've worn out your welcome, Prince Abooboo.

1110
01:02:38,739 --> 01:02:40,172
你...
[muffled] Why, you...

1111
01:02:40,241 --> 01:02:43,505
要保证让他永远消失
Make sure he's never found.

1112
01:02:46,013 --> 01:02:46,080
[laughing]

1113
01:02:46,080 --> 01:02:47,672
[laughing]

1114
01:03:25,953 --> 01:03:29,081
这魔法从没失效过.我正在洗澡时 正有人摩擦神灯
Never fails. Get in the bath and there's a rub at the lamp.

1115
01:03:29,156 --> 01:03:31,716
你好?阿尔
Hello? Al?

1116
01:03:31,792 --> 01:03:34,454
阿尔!振作点.
[gasping] Al! Kid, snap out of it.

1117
