You have to say, "Genie, I want you to save my life."' Got it?

1119
01:03:42,470 --> 01:03:44,802
快点,阿拉丁!
Come on, Aladdin!

1120
01:03:44,872 --> 01:03:47,363
那算你同意了
I'll take that as a yes. [imitating alarm]

1121
01:03:47,441 --> 01:03:49,306
全速上浮
Up scope.

1122
01:03:49,377 --> 01:03:52,175
[babbling in German]

1123
01:03:55,216 --> 01:03:57,241
[coughing]

1124
01:03:58,953 --> 01:04:01,615
别再吓我了
Don't you scare me like that.

1125
01:04:01,689 --> 01:04:04,283
精灵,我...
Genie, I, uh...

1126
01:04:04,358 --> 01:04:05,484
I...
I...

1127
