茉莉
[Sultan] Jasmine.

1132
01:04:23,511 --> 01:04:27,777
父亲,我刚经历了一次美妙的时刻
Oh, Father, I just had the most wonderful time.

1133
01:04:27,848 --> 01:04:31,011
