- [gasping] - You're speechless, I see.

1137
01:04:40,194 --> 01:04:42,059
你会是一个好妻子的
A fine quality in a wife.

1138
01:04:42,129 --> 01:04:43,994
我永远也不会嫁给你
I will never marry you.

1139
01:04:44,065 --> 01:04:47,831
-父亲,我选择阿里王子 -阿里王子已经走了
- Father, I choose Prince Ali. - Prince Ali left.

1140
01:04:47,902 --> 01:04:50,166
你最好再去检查一下水晶球,贾法尔.
Better check your crystal ball again, Jafar.

1141
01:04:50,237 --> 01:04:51,966
阿里王子!
- Prince Ali! - [gasping]

1142
01:04:52,039 --> 01:04:54,701
