1186
01:06:45,986 --> 01:06:49,114
他彻底崩溃了,他已经疯了
Oh, boy. He's cracked. He's gone nuts.

1187
01:06:49,190 --> 01:06:51,317
贾法尔!贾法尔!
Jafar! Jafar!

1188
01:06:51,392 --> 01:06:52,791
抓紧点!
Get a grip!

1189
01:06:53,761 --> 01:06:54,750
太紧了
Good grip.

1190
01:06:54,829 --> 01:06:58,765
阿里王子只不过是那个毛孩子,阿拉丁
Prince Ali is nothing more than that ragged urchin, Aladdin.

1191
01:06:58,866 --> 01:07:02,063
-他有神灯,拉戈. -那个可怜的...
- He has the lamp, lago. - Why, that miserable...

1192
01:07:02,103 --> 01:07:04,901
你要从他身上把它偷出来
But you are going to relieve him of it.

1193
01:07:04,972 --> 01:07:05,961
我?
Me?

1194
01:07:09,877 --> 01:07:11,811
国王?
Sultan?

1195
01:07:11,879 --> 01:07:14,006
他们想让我当国王?
They want me to be Sultan?

1196
01:07:14,715 --> 01:07:16,080
Huzzah!

1197
01:07:16,150 --> 01:07:18,914
向伟大的英雄致敬
 Hail the conquering hero

1198
01:07:18,986 --> 01:07:22,615
