1199
01:07:26,594 --> 01:07:29,563
阿拉丁,你已经赢得了公主的芳心
Aladdin, you've just won the heart of the princess.

1200
01:07:29,630 --> 01:07:31,757
下一步你打算做什么?
What are you gonna do next?

1201
01:07:35,569 --> 01:07:36,934
