下一步你该说"我打算给精灵自由."
[whispering] Psst. Your line is, "I'm going to free the genie."'

1203
01:07:42,810 --> 01:07:43,868
什么时候都行
Anytime.

1204
01:07:43,944 --> 01:07:47,311
-精灵.我不能 -你当然行.
- Genie. I can't. - Sure you can.

1205
01:07:47,381 --> 01:07:50,908
