1225
01:08:48,709 --> 01:08:50,939
我...对不起
[Aladdin] Look, I... I'm sorry.

1226
01:08:51,011 --> 01:08:53,070
阿布,对不起.我不是...
Abu, I'm sorry. I didn't...

1227
