1270
01:10:59,640 --> 01:11:01,665
[cackling]

1271
01:11:01,742 --> 01:11:04,905
贾法尔,你这个卑鄙的叛徒
Jafar, you vile betrayer.

1272
01:11:04,978 --> 01:11:07,947
应该说是卑鄙的国王叛徒
That's Sultan Vile Betrayer to you.

1273
01:11:08,015 --> 01:11:10,108
我们走着瞧
Oh, yeah? We'll just see about that.

1274
01:11:10,184 --> 01:11:13,085
神灯
- [gasps] The lamp. - [Jafar laughs]

1275
01:11:13,153 --> 01:11:16,520
发现者,监护者,阿布布
Finders keepers, Abooboo.

1276
01:11:22,596 --> 01:11:24,257
[whistles]

1277
01:11:25,599 --> 01:11:27,533
[people screaming]

1278
01:11:31,839 --> 01:11:33,466
精灵,不!
Genie, no!

1279
01:11:33,540 --> 01:11:37,135
对不起,孩子 我现在有了新主人
Sorry, kid. I got a new master now.

1280
01:11:37,211 --> 01:11:40,408
贾法尔,我命令你马上停止
Jafar, I order you to stop.

1281
01:11:40,481 --> 01:11:42,608
可是现在有了新的王法
Ah, but there's a new order now.

1282
01:11:42,683 --> 01:11:44,480
我的王法
My order.

1283
01:11:44,551 --> 01:11:47,611
最终,你会拜倒在我的脚下
Finally, you will bow to me.

1284
01:11:47,688 --> 01:11:49,622
我们决不低头
We will never bow to you.

1285
01:11:49,690 --> 01:11:51,817
这我一点也不奇怪?
Why am I not surprised?

1286
01:11:51,892 --> 01:11:54,360
如果你不愿跪倒在国王面前
If you won't bow before a sultan,

1287
01:11:54,428 --> 01:11:57,625
那么你会在巫师面前发抖!
then you will cower before a sorcerer!

1288
01:11:57,731 --> 01:11:59,995
精灵,我的第二个愿望...
Genie, my second wish...

1289
01:12:00,033 --> 01:12:04,436
我要成为世界上法力最强的巫师!
I wish to be the most powerful sorcerer in the world!

1290
01:12:06,273 --> 01:12:08,571
精灵,停下!
- [Jafar laughs maniacally] - Genie, stop!

1291
01:12:08,642 --> 01:12:11,577
女士们,先生们
Ladies and gentlemen,

1292
01:12:11,645 --> 01:12:17,174
多情的阿古拉巴将欢迎巫师贾法尔!
a warm Agrabah welcome for Sorcerer Jafar!

1293
01:12:17,251 --> 01:12:19,242
刚才,我们说到哪儿?
Now, where were we?

1294
01:12:19,319 --> 01:12:23,949
对.卑躬屈膝
Ah, yes. Abject humiliation.

1295
01:12:25,359 --> 01:12:29,295
走开
- Down, boy. - [meows]

1296
01:12:29,363 --> 01:12:30,625
公主
Oh, Princess.

1297
01:12:30,697 --> 01:12:33,598
我非常想给你介绍一个人
There's someone I'm dying to introduce you to.

1298
01:12:33,667 --> 01:12:35,259
贾法尔.把你的手拿开
Jafar. Get your hands off her.

1299
01:12:35,335 --> 01:12:37,326
阿里王子,对,就是他
 Prince Ali Yes, it is he

1300
01:12:37,404 --> 01:12:39,531
可他不是你了解的那个
 But not as you know him

1301
01:12:39,606 --> 01:12:43,838
看着我的嘴,我要告诉你真相
 Read my lips And come to grips with reality

1302
01:12:45,012 --> 01:12:47,037
是的,回想一下过去
 Yes, meet a blast from your past

1303
01:12:47,114 --> 01:12:49,605
谁的谎言编的这么好
 Whose lies were too good to last

1304
01:12:49,683 --> 01:12:53,141
向亲爱的阿里王子问声好
 Say hello To your precious Prince Ali

1305
01:12:53,220 --> 01:12:55,814
或者我们应该叫他阿拉丁?
Or should we say Aladdin?

1306
01:12:55,923 --> 01:12:56,912
阿里?
Ali?

1307
01:12:56,957 --> 01:13:00,188
茉莉,我曾想告诉你 我只是...
Jasmine, I tried to tell you. I'm just...

1308
01:13:00,260 --> 01:13:04,697
阿里王子其实只是阿拉丁
 So Ali turns out to be Merely Aladdin

1309
01:13:04,765 --> 01:13:06,892
这只是个骗术,还要我继续吗
 Just a con, need I go on

1310
01:13:06,967 --> 01:13:09,265
相信我
 Take it from me

1311
01:13:09,336 --> 01:13:11,634
他品行恶劣
 His personality flaws

1312
01:13:11,705 --> 01:13:13,730
给了我充分的理由
 Give me adequate cause

1313
01:13:13,807 --> 01:13:16,708
让他收拾行李来一次单程旅行
 To send him packing On a one-way trip

1314
01:13:16,777 --> 01:13:19,143
他的命运将急转直下
 So his prospects Take a terminal dip

1315
01:13:19,213 --> 01:13:24,378
他的财产被冻结, 他要被送到在世界的尽头
 His assets frozen, the venue chosen Is the ends of the earth, whoopee!

1316
01:13:24,451 --> 01:13:26,851
-再见! -再见,再见.
- So long! - Good-bye, see ya.

1317
01:13:26,920 --> 01:13:30,947
前阿里王子
 Ex-Prince Ali 

1318
01:13:32,426 --> 01:13:34,257
[laughing maniacally]

1319
01:13:52,079 --> 01:13:53,910
[wind howling]

1320
01:13:53,981 --> 01:13:55,539
[shivering]

1321
01:13:56,550 --> 01:13:58,643
阿布
Abu.

1322
01:14:00,254 --> 01:14:01,915
阿布!
Abu!

1323
01:14:02,856 --> 01:14:04,824
[Abu whimpering]

1324
01:14:05,692 --> 01:14:08,092
这都是我的错
Oh, this is all my fault.

1325
01:14:08,161 --> 01:14:12,359
我应该放了精灵 我曾有过机会.阿布
I should have freed the genie when I had the chance. Abu.

1326
01:14:12,432 --> 01:14:15,890
你没事吧?
- Are you okay? - [teeth chattering] Mm-hmm.

1327
01:14:15,969 --> 01:14:17,903
对不起,阿布.
I'm sorry, Abu.

1328
01:14:17,971 --> 01:14:20,701
事情全让我给搞砸了
I made a mess of everything.

1329
01:14:20,774 --> 01:14:24,369
也许...我应该回去把它纠正过来
Somehow... I gotta go back and set things right.

1330
01:14:31,885 --> 01:14:34,217
飞毯
Carpet.

1331
01:14:34,288 --> 01:14:37,416
- [Abu chitters] - [Aladdin strains]

1332
01:14:38,091 --> 01:14:39,956
阿布,快来挖
Abu, start digging.

1333
01:14:40,027 --> 01:14:41,153
[frantic panting]

1334
01:14:42,396 --> 01:14:44,261
就是它
That's it.

1335
01:15:01,548 --> 01:15:04,517
好了!
Yeah! All right!

1336
01:15:04,585 --> 01:15:06,610
[whines]

1337
01:15:09,756 --> 01:15:12,691
现在,我们回阿古拉巴 出发
Now, back to Agrabah. Let's go.

1338
01:15:15,596 --> 01:15:18,326
你这个木偶国王要不要来点饼干?
- [lago] Puppet ruler want a cracker? - [Sultan moaning]

1339
01:15:18,398 --> 01:15:21,196
这是你的饼干,给我全都紫氯
Here's your cracker. Shoved all the way down your throat.

1340
01:15:21,268 --> 01:15:22,599
这儿,还有更多
Here. Have lots.

1341
01:15:22,669 --> 01:15:26,298
停下.贾法尔,放开他
Stop it. Jafar, leave him alone.

1342
01:15:26,373 --> 01:15:28,273
[growling]

1343
01:15:28,342 --> 01:15:32,403
茉莉看见你变成这样我很难过
It pains me to see you reduced to this, Jasmine.

1344
01:15:34,314 --> 01:15:36,782
象你这样一朵沙漠中的美丽之花
A beautiful desert bloom such as yourself

1345
01:15:36,850 --> 01:15:40,718
应该投入世界上最有权势的男人的怀抱
should be on the arm of the most powerful man in the world.

1346
01:15:40,787 --> 01:15:42,721
你说什么,亲爱的?
What do you say, my dear?

1347
01:15:42,789 --> 01:15:45,553
如果你同意成为我的王后...
Why, with you as my queen...

1348
01:15:45,626 --> 01:15:47,685
休想
- Never. - [enraged growl]

1349
01:15:47,761 --> 01:15:50,423
我会教你如何尊重我
I'll teach you some respect.

1350
01:15:50,497 --> 01:15:51,725
[喘息声]
[gasping]

1351
01:15:53,233 --> 01:15:55,394
不.精灵.
No. Genie.

1352
01:15:56,470 --> 01:15:58,995
我决定许最后一个愿
I have decided to make my final wish.

1353
01:15:59,072 --> 01:16:02,064
我要让茉莉公主
I wish for Princess Jasmine

1354
01:16:02,142 --> 01:16:05,134
发狂地爱上我
to fall desperately in love with me.

1355
01:16:10,917 --> 01:16:14,910
主人,还有些附加条件, 有一些限制...
Ah, Master, there are a few addendas, some quid pro quo...

1356
01:16:14,988 --> 01:16:17,047
别跟我顶嘴,你这个兰色的傻大个
Don't talk back to me, you big blue lout.

1357
01:16:17,124 --> 01:16:22,152
奴仆,你必须照我说的做
[Jafar] You will do what I order you to do, slave.

1358
01:16:22,229 --> 01:16:25,164
贾法尔.
[Jasmine] Jafar.

1359
01:16:25,232 --> 01:16:31,137
我从来不知道... 你有这么英俊
I never realized how... incredibly handsome you are.

1360
01:16:32,806 --> 01:16:35,570
这还不错
Mmm. That's better.

1361
01:16:36,576 --> 01:16:39,374
现在,小可爱...
Now, pussycat...

1362
01:16:39,446 --> 01:16:42,438
告诉我我这人怎么样
tell me more about myself.

1363
01:16:42,516 --> 01:16:45,542
你个子很高...
You're tall...

1364
01:16:45,619 --> 01:16:47,951
隐秘...
dark...

1365
01:16:48,021 --> 01:16:50,046
衣冠楚楚...
well dressed...

1366
01:16:50,123 --> 01:16:52,455
小朋友
Al. Al, little buddy.

1367
01:16:52,526 --> 01:16:55,086
嘘
Shh.

1368
01:16:57,264 --> 01:16:58,959
我无法帮你
Al, I can't help you.

1369
01:16:59,032 --> 01:17:01,796
我现在为那个神经病工作 你想做什么?
I work for Senor Psychopath now. What are you gonna do?

1370
01:17:01,868 --> 01:17:05,929
我是个叫化子,还记得吗? 我要来个即兴表演
Hey, I'm a street rat, remember? I'll improvise.

1371
01:17:06,006 --> 01:17:09,567
你的牙是那么的可爱
[Jasmine]...cute little gaps between your teeth.

1372
01:17:09,643 --> 01:17:11,577
继续说
Go on.

1373
01:17:11,645 --> 01:17:14,170
还有你的头...
And your beard...

1374
01:17:14,247 --> 01:17:17,410
是那么的...弯弯曲曲
is so... twisted.

1375
01:17:18,452 --> 01:17:22,786
你已经偷走了我的心 贾法...!
- You've stolen my heart. - [gasping] Jaf...!

1376
01:17:22,856 --> 01:17:26,553
还有那个叫化子?
- [lago mumbling] - And the street rat?

1377
01:17:26,626 --> 01:17:29,356
什么叫化子?
What street rat?

1378
01:17:31,965 --> 01:17:34,024
- [clattering] - [gasping]

1379
01:17:35,736 --> 01:17:37,135
[gasping]

1380
01:17:38,138 --> 01:17:39,127
[both] Yech!

1381
01:17:40,407 --> 01:17:42,466
那是...
That was...

1382
01:17:44,745 --> 01:17:45,734
是你!
You!

1383
01:17:47,147 --> 01:17:51,106
我要杀你几次才行,小子?
How many times do I have to kill you, boy?

1384
01:17:54,054 --> 01:17:55,612
快拿神灯.
Get the lamp.

1385
01:17:57,157 --> 01:17:58,749
不!
No!

1386
01:17:58,825 --> 01:18:01,487
公主 你的时间用完了
Ah, ah, ah, Princess. Your time is up.

1387
01:18:01,561 --> 01:18:03,961
[growling]

1388
01:18:05,665 --> 01:18:07,394
茉莉
Jasmine.

1389
01:18:08,068 --> 01:18:10,229
干的好,贾法...
Oh, nice shot, Jaf...

1390
01:18:11,772 --> 01:18:14,172
别想耍我
Don't toy with me.

1391
01:18:15,075 --> 01:18:16,702
阿布!
Abu!

1392
01:18:16,777 --> 01:18:20,110
小子,事情都清楚了
[Jafar] Things are unraveling fast now, boy.

1393
01:18:20,180 --> 01:18:22,944
[Jafar laughing]

1394
01:18:23,016 --> 01:18:24,711
找到关键了吗?
Get the point?

1395
01:18:24,785 --> 01:18:26,548
[laughing]

1396
01:18:26,620 --> 01:18:28,281
[straining]

1397
01:18:30,757 --> 01:18:33,385
我只不过是热了热身
I'm just getting warmed up.

1398
01:18:35,729 --> 01:18:39,028
你不敢自己跟我较量一下吗, 你这个胆小的毒蛇?
Are you afraid to fight me yourself, you cowardly snake?

1399
01:18:39,099 --> 01:18:39,199
一条毒蛇,我是吗?
A snake, am l?
A snake, am l?

1400
01:18:39,199 --> 01:18:42,032
一条毒蛇,我是吗?

1401
01:18:42,102 --> 01:18:46,903
也许应该让你看看我是如何成为毒蛇的
Perhaps you'd like to see how snakelike I can be.

1402
01:19:02,989 --> 01:19:04,251
[screaming]

1403
01:19:04,324 --> 01:19:06,588
一二三四五六七 将那宝剑刺进蛇
 Rick 'em, rack 'em, rock 'em, rake Stick that sword into that snake

1404
01:19:06,660 --> 01:19:08,218
这件事你别插手
You stay out of this.

1405
01:19:08,295 --> 01:19:12,696
贾法尔,贾法尔,他是我的偶像 如果他真能做到的话...太棒了!
Jafar, Jafar, he's our man. If he can't do it... great!

1406
01:19:16,002 --> 01:19:17,629
阿拉丁
[Jasmine] Aladdin.

1407
01:19:23,844 --> 01:19:25,106
[screams]

1408
01:19:27,147 --> 01:19:29,411
茉莉,支持住
Jasmine, hang on.

1409
01:19:30,951 --> 01:19:34,751
你这小傻瓜
[laughing] You little fool.

1410
01:19:35,755 --> 01:19:40,124
你认为你可以击败这世界上最强大的人吗
You thought you could defeat the most powerful being on Earth.

1411
01:19:41,194 --> 01:19:44,459
勒死他,贾法尔. 勒死他就象...
Squeeze him, Jafar. Squeeze him like a... Awk!

1412
01:19:44,531 --> 01:19:48,558
没了精灵,小子,你就什么也不是
Without the genie, boy, you're nothing.

1413
01:19:48,635 --> 01:19:51,798
精灵.精灵.
The genie. The genie.

1414
01:19:51,872 --> 01:19:54,739
精灵比你的法力强多了
The genie has more power than you'll ever have.

1415
01:19:54,808 --> 01:19:55,832
什么?
What?

1416
01:19:55,909 --> 01:19:58,309
你的法力是他给的,他也可以收回去
He gave you your power. He can take it away.

1417
01:19:58,378 --> 01:20:01,108
你在干什么? 为什么把我扯进来?
Al, what are you doing? Why are you bringing me into this?

1418
01:20:01,181 --> 01:20:04,947
面对现实吧,贾法尔 你只能做老二
Face it, Jafar. You're still just second best.

1419
01:20:05,018 --> 01:20:07,384
你说的对
You're right.

1420
01:20:07,454 --> 01:20:11,220
他的法力确实比我强
His power does exceed my own.

1421
01:20:11,291 --> 01:20:13,418
但这不会太久的
But not for long.

1422
01:20:13,493 --> 01:20:16,621
那孩子是疯了 他被打晕了
The boy is crazy. He's a little punch-drunk.

1423
01:20:16,696 --> 01:20:18,288
他被蛇打的太重了
One too many hits with the snake.

1424
01:20:18,365 --> 01:20:21,266
奴仆,我要许我的第三个愿望
Slave, I make my third wish.

1425
01:20:21,334 --> 01:20:25,600
我想做一个万能的精灵
I wish to be an all-powerful genie!

1426
01:20:29,276 --> 01:20:33,042
你的愿望就是我的命令 干的好
All right, your wish is my command. Way to go, Al.

1427
01:20:39,119 --> 01:20:40,746
Yes.

1428
01:20:40,820 --> 01:20:43,653
Yes!

1429
01:20:43,723 --> 01:20:45,350
法力
The power.

1430
01:20:45,425 --> 01:20:48,417
- [Jafar laughs] - [Jasmine coughs]

1431
01:20:48,495 --> 01:20:52,363
无敌的法力!
The absolute power!

1432
01:20:53,199 --> 01:20:55,667
-你做了什么啊? -相信我
- What have you done? - Trust me.

1433
01:20:56,670 --> 01:21:00,868
宇宙将由我来控制
The universe is mine to command, to control!

1434
01:21:02,008 --> 01:21:04,772
不要太性急,贾法尔. 你没忘了什么吗?
Not so fast, Jafar. Aren't you forgetting something?

1435
01:21:04,844 --> 01:21:07,108
你想成为精灵...
- Huh? - You wanted to be a genie...

1436
01:21:07,180 --> 01:21:08,477
你办到了
you got it.

1437
01:21:08,548 --> 01:21:09,810
什么?
What?

1438
01:21:09,883 --> 01:21:12,215
任何事都有它自己的法则
And everything that goes with it.

1439
01:21:12,285 --> 01:21:15,846
-不!不! -我要离开这
- No! No! - I'm gettin' out of here.

1440
01:21:15,922 --> 01:21:17,947
拥有宇宙间无穷的力量...
[Aladdin] Phenomenal cosmic powers...

1441
01:21:18,024 --> 01:21:21,152
你是个精灵.我不想...
You're the genie. I don't want...

1442
01:21:21,227 --> 01:21:22,529
却必须挤在小小的灯里
Itty bitty living space.

1443
01:21:22,829 --> 01:21:25,821
阿尔,你这个小天才
Al, you little genius, you.

1444
01:21:33,406 --> 01:21:35,465
- Ahh! - [meow]

1445
01:21:40,714 --> 01:21:43,316
[贾法尔]把你的臭嘴从我的脸上挪开
[Jafar] Get your blasted beak out of my face.

1446
01:21:43,316 --> 01:21:46,653
-[拉戈]闭嘴,你这个笨蛋 -别对我说闭嘴
- [lago] Oh, shut up, you moron. - Don't tell me to shut up.

1447
01:21:46,653 --> 01:21:47,984
让我来
Allow me.

1448
01:21:48,054 --> 01:21:52,423
在奇幻谷住上一万年 会让他安静下来的
10,000 years in a Cave ofWonders ought to chill him out.

1449
01:21:52,492 --> 01:21:56,724
- [lago yelling, indistinct] - [Jafar] Shut up!

1450
01:22:01,968 --> 01:22:03,868
茉莉...
Jasmine...

1451
01:22:03,937 --> 01:22:07,429
对不起我向你撒了谎 说我是王子
I'm sorry I lied to you about being a prince.

1452
01:22:07,507 --> 01:22:10,169
我理解你为什么那么说
I know why you did.

1453
01:22:10,243 --> 01:22:12,905
我想...
Well, I guess...

1454
01:22:12,979 --> 01:22:15,948
要说再见了?
this is good-bye?

